(22, 'Velux Loft Conversion', 'Velux Loft Conversion is also known as the Roof-light loft conversion ', '<strong>Velux Loft Conversion is Cost-Effective and the Simplest Conversion!</strong>', 'Velux Loft Conversions Company in London', '<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Are you planning to expand your property and inquisitive to know how to entirely utilize the space? The answer might be here with us! Velux Loft Conversion London. We know that no two loft conversions will be the same, and that is why we provide a service that caters to the specifications of each customer.&nbsp;By installing Velux windows on either side of a sloped roof, we give you an ideal result that determines value, reliability, and credibility.</span></p>\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">\n	<strong>VELUX LOFT CONVERSION LONDON - AN IDEAL WAY TO CONVERT YOUR &lsquo;HOUSE&rsquo; INTO &lsquo;HOME&rsquo;.</strong></h1>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">At Loft Conversion London, we provide Velux Loft Conversions, which is one of the most popular and simplest of all Loft conversions. It is the most cost effective soluton to increase internal house space in the loft, moreover it does not even require planning permission. When compared to other loft conversion types, such as dormer, mansard, hip to gable, the Velux loft conversion requires very little construction and little disruption too. The velux loft conversion is also known as Roof light loft conversion or Skylight.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><img alt="" src="	https://loftconversionlondon.com/upload/20200611141844velux-loft-conversion-watford.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 333px;" /></span></p>\n<h2>\n	<strong>What is Velux Loft Conversions London?</strong></h2>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Velux Loft Conversions is unquestionably one of the easiest and affordable solutions to add extra headroom to utilize the space available. It also helps you gain additional natural light 