(66, 'Loft Conversion Isleworth', 'Loft and Attic Conversions in Isleworth', '<strong>Looking to Convert your Loft in Isleworth?</strong>', 'Loft Conversions Company in Isleworth, West London', '<h1>\n	<strong>Loft Conversion Isleworth</strong></h1>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Located on the west of river Thames, and east of the town Hounslow, Isleworth is a small town in west London. Isleworth is known as a peaceful, pleasant and quiet city, with a significant population located alongside the River Thames.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Isleworth is a well-cultivated farming and trading establishment, with approx 118 households, it has been held as a centre of power and revenue.</span></p>\n<h2>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><strong>Why Loft conversion?</strong></span></h2>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">A loft conversion is a considerable change in your property and truly transforms what you are dreaming for your home.</span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;">Increase your house value - There are plenty of things you can do to increase your house value, though loft conversion is a widely recognised way of boosting a house value by up to 20%. If you compare the increased value of your loft conversion, the rewards are apparent.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;">Expand the space of your property -&nbsp; There is most of the time when we think to have extra space, and a loft conversion gives you an opportunity to with the benefit of extra space to serve whatever purpose you need it for. Turn it into a playroom for your young, storage room, office space, once you have that space, do whatever you want.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;">Save your money -&nbsp; Rather than relocation, a loft conversion can save your plenty of time and money. Moving to the house requires a huge amount of money and an immense amount of time and afford. Loft conversion not only saves you from all these hassles, it also gives you a significant return on your investments.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;">Avoid major disruption -&nbsp; Apart from the financial requirements, moving to a new house, you may face with the major upheaval of packing, loading and moving of your boxes and belongings and then unpacking the whole stuff is so daunting. Loft conversion saves all of your trouble and leaves you with the improved space to enjoy.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n	<img alt="" src="https://loftconversionlondon.com/upload/20200803145920loft-conversion-value.jpg" style="width: 600px; height: 408px;" /></p>\n<h3>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">What can the extra room be used for?</span></h3>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">With a little imagination and some creative design work, the lost conversion can transform your house into something you would be proud of.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Most common types of a loft conversion are -</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size: 22px;">TV Room -&nbsp; If you have a teenager at your home, a separate room for entertainment is an ideal way to avoid rows over who will watch what.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size: 22px;">Children playroom -&nbsp; Toddlers need a sufficient space to play, and certainly need a bigger space to let off all the steam. Loft can be a great way to convert space into a useful playground area, where your kids can run freely, though you need to conform to insulation requirements.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size: 22px;">Guest bedroom -&nbsp; Most of the average middle-class families do not have any separate guest bedroom. No doubt this is the reason, a guest bedroom is becoming a fast-growing most popular oft conversion choice for many families. With adding a little extra cost, in the guest bedroom, you can also include a small basin, walk-in-shower as an ideal accompaniment.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size: 22px; text-align: center;">Bathroom -&nbsp; Surprisingly, as per our loft conversion Isleworth team, most of the lofts are being turned into extra bathrooms, especially where teenagers and guests are concerned. Ensure to have enough headroom with sufficient water pressure.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><img alt="" src="https://loftconversionlondon.com/upload/20200804140513loft-conversion-bathroom7.jpg" style="font-size: 22px; text-align: center; width: 600px; height: 400px;" /></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size: 22px;">Office -&nbsp; Every year, a hundred entrepreneurs start their startups from home and need a specific space to work. Also, all thanks to the latest technologies, who inspire more and more people to opt for work from home, the Loft can be the ideal office for them. Installing a phone extension and a computer does not present any problems.</span></p>\n<h3>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><strong>Types of Loft Conversions Isleworth - </strong></span></h3>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<a href="https://loftconversionlondon.com/dormer-loft-conversion"><span style="font-size:22px;">Dormer Conversions</span></a></li>\n	<li>\n		<a href="https://loftconversionlondon.com/mansard-loft-conversion"><span style="font-size:22px;">Mansard Conversions</span></a></li>\n	<li>\n		<a href="https://loftconversionlondon.com/velux-loft-conversion"><span style="font-size:22px;">Velux Conversions</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><strong>Dormer Conversion -</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">It is a type of an existing roof conversion, and offers an additional floor space and headroom. Dormers extrude from the roof slope and typically get built at the rear of the property with a variety of styles. Inside, it has a horizontal ceiling and vertical walls connected to the usual slanting sides of a conversion. Dormer Loft conversion will provide you with an additional space that can make a conversion feasible. However, it does not look so attractive but can provide you with enough internal space and maybe cost more due to complexity.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><img alt="" src="https://loftconversionlondon.com/upload/20200804143841dormer-loft-conversion-isleworth.jpg" style="width: 600px; height: 450px;" /></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><strong>Mansard Conversion -</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">With the lower upward slope and the straight section of the roof, Mansard conversion, maximising the available space within your Loft. Although Flat roof dormers tend to be a more popular choice across London, Mansard Conversion is worth considering to maximise your space. In a few conversion types, it may require planning permission.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><img alt="" src="https://loftconversionlondon.com/upload/20200528184811mansard-loft-conversion-barnet.jpg" style="width: 600px; height: 300px;" /></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><strong>Velux Conversions </strong>&nbsp;-</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Velux conservation is the most cost-effective, quick and straightforward conversion type, and generally, it does not require any planning permission. The Velux windows generally get used to fit flush with the line of the roof while leaving the existing roof structure untouched. It would be the best choice if you have enough headroom with a&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 22px;">minimal disruption or delays due to bad weather.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n	<span style="font-size: 22px;"><img alt="" src="https://loftconversionlondon.com/upload/20200804144035loft-conversion-isleworth-velux.jpg" style="width: 600px; height: 400px;" /></span></p>\n<h3>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><strong>Cost of loft conversion -</strong></span></h3>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">The cost can vary enormously for each type of conversion. Conversion cost often depends on two conditions.</span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;">Where you live</span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;">What you want to be done</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">However, an average loft conversion can cost you around &pound;35,000 to &pound;45,000, excluding surface and fittings.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><img alt="" src="https://loftconversionlondon.com/upload/20200804144213loft-conversion-isleworth-ideas.jpg" style="width: 600px; height: 900px;" /></span></p>\n<h3>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><strong>How to choose a builder?</strong></span></h3>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">It&#39;s always suggested, start hiring a builder with a recommendation. In local forums offering you can find plenty of builder details.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">However, Loft conversion Isleworth can help you to come up with a perfect loft conversion with quality and at a very cost-effective price.</span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;">We have a dedicated and highly skilled team of professionals who will stay alongside with you during the entire project work.</span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;">We serve you with quality and trustworthy services.</span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;">We always keep you updated at each stage about the procedure and take your consent before doing anything.</span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;">If you have any questions and doubts, you are always welcome to contact us.</span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;">We do not bother you unnecessarily in any work. Our work process gives you complete peace of mind, and you can observe the entire job while relaxing on your chair.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Are you interested to see your Loft converted? Get in touch with us today for non-obligation quotations and any suggestions.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><strong>Inspiring&nbsp; loft conversion ideas for your Isleworth home</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Isleworth is a great place to live in. If you are craving for extra space or have it already but not sure how to use it, our inspiring loft conversion ideas can help you to turn that place into a beautiful space that you always desire. A well-designed loft room not only creates extra habitable space that helps to free up a busy household, but it also builds the opportunity for a fashionable and unique space.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Before starting working on a loft conversion Isleworth, it&#39;s vital to keep all the ideas in one place. A loft conversion is not just a structure; it is your room configuration, budget, positioning of your doors, windows and furniture and of course your energy efficiency that must be considered.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Find out the best loft conversion ideas that will have your creative juices flowing and loving your new space.</span></p>\n<h3>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><strong>CREATE AN EXTRA BEDROOM -</strong></span></h3>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">If you have a spare room in your loft, you can use it by creating an extra bedroom for your guests. This extra room can add much-needed living space to your existing floor plan.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">However, before starting to work on conversion, you should consider a few things such as space utilization and determine whether or not you need to add insulation, drywall etc. Choosing a light or neutral colour palette for painting the walls can enhance the room&#39;s beauty and make the room look larger. Opting for furniture with storage options built-in can also improve the functionality of your loft. Go for a roof window for nice natural light.</span></p>\n<h2>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><strong>KIDS ROOMS ARE PERFECT IN THE LOFT -</strong></span></h2>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Not having enough head height in the loft is the most challenging thing which we often face. At least 2.2 metres at the highest point has been considered as an ideal height for a comfortable living room. So if you are struggling with the height, you can turn that space into a kids room. This area could be their playroom where they can keep their toys and keep the rest of the house clutter-free. Extra beds could be built into the walls leaving the floor space open so they can spend some good time with their friends here.</span></p>\n<h3>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><strong>EXTRA BATHROOM -</strong></span></h3>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Having an extra bathroom is excellent for convenience. If you have enough room, it would be a great option to add some luxury in your bathroom facilities. Adding an extra bathroom also increases the value of your house by as much as 10.5 per cent.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Place a freestanding bath under the slope as loft spaces often have low ceilings or if you are connecting it to a master bedroom, it would be beneficial to keep an open floor plan. A shower will be a great idea if you have enough height. Make it simple with some clean lines, traditional colour palette or with wood furnishing which can make your new loft space feel all the more open and authentic.</span></p>\n<h3>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><strong>A HOME LIBRARY -</strong></span></h3>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">If you have a book lever, adding a space for your books would be a great addition. You can create a finished wall of bookshelves or can utilize your old shelves between the roof beams to create a rustic look. Add some cosy seating area to complete a nice little reading look where you can spend some of your quality time.</span></p>\n<h3>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><strong>CREATE A MULTIPURPOSE ROOM -</strong></span></h3>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">A loft conversion is a great way to utilize your wasted space to turn into a useful place. In Isleworth, it can add around 11% more value to your place, and if you have frequent guests staying, it can make your life easier. So, even if you do not have any planning to use it for days; it can still be a significant investment.</span></p>\n<h3>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><strong>A PLACE TO FULFILL YOUR HOBBIES -</strong></span></h3>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Most of us miss our hobbies due not to have sufficient space. However, a loft can add that perfect place for you. You can create a game room or home cinema or a music room. Create a soundproof room if you are planning for some activities which might be too noisy to keep next door happy. Add acoustic mineral woods between the floor joints, and thermal insulation to the walls to muffle the sound.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><strong>A HOME OFFICE -</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Now when most people are opting for work from home, converting your empty loft space into something productive can be a great idea. Depending on the space you have, you can create a built-in desk and utilize the natural light and air from the roof window. Also, if you have children, it would be an excellent option for a quiet workspace. Plus if you can look outdoors, if you need any metal break.</span></p>\n<h3>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><strong>ADD SOME LIGHT AND DRAMA -</strong></span></h3>\n<h3>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">You have enough budget, you can add some WOW factors and architectural glazing. Instead of using chandeliers or pendant lights, opt for small colourful LED lights. As chandeliers or pendant lights take too much space and could limit the movement inside. Use beam light as it will take care of enhancing the pleasant structure of the ceiling. Illuminate the space with beautiful side lamps and wall lightings.</span></h3>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Working with Loft conversion Isleworth is very convenient and gives excellent value for money. Whatever design you choose should meet your requirements and sure to be the perfect choice for the family.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">&nbsp;Be sure to visit &nbsp;loft conversion isleworth to give your loft space a new identity.</span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '', 'Loft Conversions Isleworth | Isleworth Loft Conversion Company                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           ', 'Looking for a Loft Conversion Company in Isleworth? We undertake all loft conversion work in Isleworth right from design to build. Contact our team today for a free estimate and site survey   \n\n	\n\n	Located on the west of river Thames, and east of the town Hounslow, Isleworth is a small town in west London. Isleworth is                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 ', 'Loft Conversion Isleworth', 'loft-conversion-isleworth', NULL, 1, '1', '1', 0, '', '', '2020-08-24'),
