ss for a loft conversion in Bexleyheath.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Take a look at our renovation process which has been broadly classified to its best&nbsp;</span></p>\n<ol>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;">UNDERSTANDING YOUR DREAM HOUSE&nbsp;&nbsp; -</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p style="margin-left:36.0pt;">\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">The specialists that we have firstly take an ample amount of time to know about your dream project and expectations. We understand your requirements, consider the restrictions, and give you the best possible layout based on your desires.</span></p>\n<ol>\n	<li value="2">\n		<span style="font-size:22px;">PLANNING AND AUTHORISATION&nbsp;&nbsp; -</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p style="margin-left:36.0pt;">\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">In order to begin, there is some paperwork in which we require your support to finish. Deliberating with the authority and completing this process as fast as we could, we pave a path to continue to your dreams.</span></p>\n<ol>\n	<li value="3">\n		<span style="font-size:22px;">WORK BEGINS!&nbsp; -</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p style="margin-left:36.0pt;">\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">With the completion of the previous tasks, our academically qualified builders, electricians, painters, plumbers, and carpenters set off to work with full passion and do not let their focus change till the very last day.</span></p>\n<h3>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><strong>OUR UNRIVALED CUSTOMER-FRIENDLY SERVICES</strong></span></h3>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Our belief in the fact that a proper companionship between the team and the company is a must makes us stand out as we design our provisions accordingly. A right serviceman must have a vision, a goal in mind. His/her commitment and passion towards the assigned tasks must reflect in their work.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">We also believe in the saying that &lsquo;communication is the key.&rsquo; Therefore, a regular and clear skill of communication with the clients and other pupils involved in the project is a must.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">And finally, an innovative and creative mind is an additional factor that adds a cherry to the top. The ability to understand the customer&rsquo;s ideas and to work following it is a skill not every contractor has.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><img alt="" src="https://loftconversionlondon.com/upload/20200818153807loft-conversion-bexleyheath.png" style="width: 600px; height: 333px;" /></span></p>\n<h2 align="center">\n	&nbsp;A brief about the suburb of Bexleyheath</h2>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">With a population of 31,929, Bexleyheath is a hamlet in the London Borough of Bexley in Greater London.ts local schools, great architecture and affordable housing price make this city a good place to live. Nationally important historic houses and just a 35 min drive from central London makes this city desirable for many families.</span></p>\n<h2>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Pros of having a loft conversion in Bexleyheath</span></h2>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Turning your dusty, unused loft into something valuable is clearly a great way to add value into your property.</span></p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;">Increase value in your property -&nbsp; A loft conversion adds up to 10-15% extra value to your property.</span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;">Extra living space - This is the biggest advantage of a loft conversion. You can utilize your extra space to turn into the desired place.</span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;">Quick Project Turnaround: An average loft conversion takes 6-8 weeks to get mature.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Appartingly, if you are thinking of doing a loft conversion, you are the right place. It&#39;s time to make better use of your loft. Our stylish loft conversion Bexleyheath ideas can help you to turn your house into a dream place to live.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Check out our inspiring loft conversion Bexleyheath ideas -</span></p>\n<h4>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">ESCAPE TO A BEAUTIFUL LIVING ROOM&nbsp; -</span></h4>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Create a perfect retreat for your house with a lovable living space in your loft. Everyone likes to spend quality time with family and friends, but also we want to spend some peaceful time just with ownself. Keep this living area casual with a classy sofa and mismatched chair. Neutral colour on walls and funky colour rugs will make it more delightful along with super cool accessories.</span></p>\n<h3>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">LOFT CONVERSION DESIGN TO EMBRACE ITS PROPORTIONS -</span></h3>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">If you have a small place or a couple of small rooms, take advantage of the natural, cosy feeling. No other colour can beat white when it comes to making the room look larger while giving it a natural and lighter look. Pair this lighting colour with dark wooden colour furniture and with a large side lamp. Ensure the room feels cosy and welcoming.</span></p>\n<h3>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">EXPOSE YOUR BRICKS -</span></h3>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">To make your bricks look more stylish, you can leave one brick wall unpainted and paint the other one with vibrant colour. That looks especially cool in an attic with slanted ceilings. If your walls are not in good shape, you can use some classy wallpapers to create the same look.</span></p>\n<h4>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">MAXIMIZE THE NATURAL DAYLIGHT&nbsp; -</span></h4>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Do not neglect the size and position of your windows as it is a vital aspect in a loft conversion. As a general thumb rule in loft conversion, if you&#39;re keen to maximize natural light, your glaze should make up 20 percent of the roof. However, the position of the window depends on the height and size of the roof. For loft conversion Bexleyheath, you can opt for a top-hung option if the window is within arm&#39;s reach as it allows an unspoiled view and more headroom, while a centre-pivot window is best if the window is out of reach.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><img alt="" src="https://loftconversionlondon.com/upload/20200526190055bungalow-loft-conversion-london.jpg" style="width: 600px; height: 241px;" /></span></p>\n<h4>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">SHOWCASE YOUR STAIRS -</span></h4>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">The staircase that leads up to your loft can take up a chunk of legroom, consider making it a focal point rather than just leaving it plain. Also, you can utilize your loft conversion stairs for bookcases, storage areas.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><img alt="" src="https://loftconversionlondon.com/upload/20200804143055gerrards-cross-loft-conversion2.jpg" style="width: 600px; height: 450px;" /></span></p>\n<h4>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">BALANCE OUT YOUR HOUSE WITH LOFT CONVERSION -</span></h4>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">If you have enough living space but lacking a bathroom and bedrooms, loft conversion would be the best option to bring your home into proportion. With an en suite bathroom, you can use this space to turn into a spare bedroom or bathroom.</span></p>\n<h4>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">CONVERT YOUR SMALL LOFT INTO A KIDS SPACE -</span></h4>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">It is common to turn your loft into a master en-suite, but converting a narrow place into a kids room would be more practical. You can also use your downstairs space to turn it into a small kids room. Accomplish this place with a few necessary furniture, as kids need more room to play freely, sleep comfortably, and have enough space for their toys.</span></p>\n<h4>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">INCORPORATE A STYLISH BATHROOM IN A LOFT CONVERSION&nbsp; -</span></h4>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Do not let Awkward dimensions and bulky beams restrict to creating a bathroom in your loft space. A shower requires a minimum amount of headroom; you can turn into a freestanding bath under a low ceiling. You can incorporate it with a traditional colour palette and work well with period architecture. The use of one sheet of unframed glass, placed by two sleek stainless-steel bars can keep this wet place unobtrusive.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><img alt="" src="https://loftconversionlondon.com/upload/20200804140623loft-conversion-bathroom4.jpg" style="width: 600px; height: 281px;" /></span></p>\n<h4>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">LEAVE YOUR LOFT OPEN -</span></h4>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Sometimes it could be a great option to leave your attic open, mostly if you do not have a proper space for windows. The open loft will provide better insulation to heat, natural light and proper ventilation. It will also add a desirable look with plenty of appeals.</span></p>\n<h4>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">BUILD IN LOW-LEVEL STORAGE -</span></h4>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Most of us have a low space between the slope of the roof and the floor, which we don&#39;t know how to use. You can turn this place into the storage room or into an elegant home office. A custom made solution combines drawers for paperwork and baskets for occasionally used items like printers.</span></p>\n<h2>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">THE SIX MAIN TYPES OF LOFT CONVERSION -</span></h2>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;"><a href="https://loftconversionlondon.com/velux-loft-conversion">Rooflight loft conversions Bexleyheath</a> -&nbsp; It requires a minimum amount of structural work and a most cost-effective loft conversion.</span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;"><a href="https://loftconversionlondon.com/hip-to-gable-loft-conversions">Hip-to-gable loft conversions Bexleyheath</a> -&nbsp; This one is a most commonly found conversion type for end-terrace or semi-detached houses.</span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;"><a href="https://loftconversionlondon.com/dormer-loft-conversion">Dormer loft conversions Bexleyheath</a> -&nbsp; Dormer loft conversion is the easiest way to add light and an increased amount of roof space with full headroom.</span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;">Gable-to-gable loft conversions Bexleyheath - Including a new box extension this conversion type spans the space between each gable end</span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;">Modular extension loft conversions Bexleyheath-&nbsp; It can be utilized where existing loft space is unsuitable for conversion.</span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:22px;"><a href="https://loftconversionlondon.com/mansard-loft-conversion">Mansard loft conversions Bexleyheath</a> -&nbsp; Create extra volume with mansard loft conversion idea. The process of this conversion, replace either one or both roof slopes with very steep sloping sides and a flat roof over the top.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">VISIT OUR WEBSITE TO KNOW MORE ABOUT US!</span></h3>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">For us, our clients stand above all, and with this promise, we continue to maintain a bond even after we hand over your renovated house to you.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Our previous customers are proof of our words! You may check out the feedback and testimonials as proof yourself, and in case still not satisfied - contact them personally!</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Other than loft conversion facilities, we also provide house extension services to various cities around the world - be it London, Wembley, Chalfont, Edgeware, etc our outreach is everywhere.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">&nbsp;For a greater degree of satisfaction, you may enquire about us by visiting our website.</span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">After making a great choice of going for Loft conversion Bexleyheath, don&rsquo;t spoil its worth by not contacting us because if there is one thing we can guarantee you above all is - TRUST!</span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '', 'Loft Conversions Bexleyheath | Bexleyheath Loft Conversion Company                                                                                                                                                                        ', 'Looking for a Loft Conversion Company in Bexleyheath? We undertake all loft conversion work in Bexleyheath right from design to build. Contact our team today for a free estimate and site survey                                                                                                                                                                ', 'Loft Conversion Bexleyheath', 'loft-conversion-bexleyheath', NULL, 1, '1', '1', 0, '', '', '2020-08-27');
