d planning permission and take so much time, a loft conversion is quick and easy to transform. It allows you to utilize your dead space without even compromising with your property.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><img alt="" src="https://loftconversionlondon.com/upload/20200526063513loftconversionlondoncinema.png" style="width: 600px; height: 398px;" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p>\n<h4>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Increase Natural Light -</span></h4>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">The loft conversion allows adding roof windows. It helps natural lights to come in, without being overshadowed with buildings and trees. As we already know that natural light has many benefits it improves our overall health and mental and physical condition, reduces headache and boosts our energy level. Loft Conversion Chalfont is a trusted attic renovation with whom you can discuss what kind of conversion could be best for your home and how you can incorporate design features that help expand the natural light into your home. All thanks to the height, positioning and angles of the windows.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n	<span style="font-size:22px;"><img alt="" src="https://loftconversionlondon.com/upload/20200526190055bungalow-loft-conversion-london.jpg" style="width: 600px; height: 241px;" /></span></p>\n<h4>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Creates A Multiple-Use Room -</span></h4>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Your newly renovated space completely depends on how you want to use it. Most of the people use their loft conversion to make an extra bedroom, though it doesn&rsquo;t necessarily mean that it&rsquo;s the only option you can opt for. If you have kids, you can turn your loft into a kids playroom filled with toys, gaming consoles and beautiful little chairs. You can also incorporate the room with different types of storage so that you can keep the rest of the home clean and clutter-free. Conversion also allows altering the room with age, as when your kids will grow up, you can utilize the room for another purpose.</span></p>\n<h4>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Easier than moving -</span></h4>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Without any doubt, a loft conversion is a more convenient option than moving. If you are purchasing a new house, you have to cover the cost of a deposit and need to spend on stamp duty, solicitor fees and surveying etc. Apart from this, along with the hassle of packing up all belongings, your kids may have to leave their school, friends and the place.</span></p>\n<h4>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Save your time and money -</span></h4>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">&nbsp;A loft conversion is a more cost-effective and time-saving alternative. A conversion work can be scheduled for any time as it does not rely on factors such as weather. Plus it does not need much labour as the external walls and roofing are already there. It only requires some fundamental changes to support brickwork and floors along with the few additions on the roof wall. Also, to make any other alterations at your home, you may need planning permission. On the other hand, unless you are not doing any major changes, in loft conversion you do not need any planning permission as you are building inside your home and it&#39;s already classed as permitted developments. It excludes the hassle and saves lots of time and fee.</span></p>\n<h4>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">Get a Room With A View -</span></h4>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:22px;">People who stay in a busy town have often only enjoyed the view of housing estates, roads and offices, which is, of course, no one likes and are quite unappealing. This is also a major reason that renovation becomes a pleasant surprise for people. Most of the loft conversion has big windows that make stargazing on clear evenings appealing. It also allows you to see your local place from a new prospect.</span></p>\n<p style="t