(5, 1, 'What are you waiting for. Fill in the above form with your website URL..', '<p>\r\n	<span class="align-justify section-paragraph"><span style="font-size:22px;">Our main goal is to get you rankings for those&nbsp; ensures that optimum quality is maintained in the work delivered. We have helped numerous small businesses over the years in securing top rankings in various search engine rankings, increase awareness about their brand amongst the masses as well as build up a social presence through various social...</span></span></p>\r\n', '201208094547img.jpg', 0, 1, '2020-12-08 09:45:27'),
